Pat Priest (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Priest_(actress) 0 Patricia Ann Priest (born August 15, 1936) is an American actress known for portraying the second Marilyn Munster on the television show, The Munsters (1964–1966) after original actress Beverley Owen left after 13 episodes.
